{"tid":2509662,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中學教師因發佈政治漫畫，裁定專業失德成立，有機會面臨釘牌。","createTime":"2021-04-29T15:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T06:27:48.000Z","uid":211994,"like":95,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"f1a0af00dfc6d8bb8d892b4d0040d9b223d377bc","tid":2509662,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:06:12.000Z","msg":"請大家㩒入去睇全文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/MRSYFVVYWVHC7PJXRGCJDSLE4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FMRSYFVVYWVHC7PJXRGCJDSLE4M%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=bdddf445\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FMRSYFVVYWVHC7PJXRGCJDSLE4M%2F&h=cdded0e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/MRSYFVVYWVHC7PJXRGCJDSLE4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n白色恐怖繼續籠罩教育界，於社交媒體創作政治漫畫的中學教師「vawongsir」（黃Sir）在其Facebook專頁表示，去年被匿名投訴指其漫畫「不恰當」，教育局指<span class=\"gold\"><strong>其10張漫畫對政府或警察作「無理」指控，裁定為專業失德投訴成立</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUjzjdRuXorv7ENZLZucn8zrmnvsTDcs3PCkTZZ2tQJ2G?filename=nukGqX9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnukGqX9.png&h=248e280c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n他至今未知最終判罰，最壞打算是下學年不能再做正職老師，惟強調不會因此滅熄對藝術的執着與熱情，希望能以創作維生。&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n阿sir嘅IG<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/COPrDNxJrSB/?igshid=1qtyu15sx2vhi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOPrDNxJrSB%2F%3Figshid%3D1qtyu15sx2vhi&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwUyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=1c897bcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOPrDNxJrSB%2F%3Figshid%3D1qtyu15sx2vhi&h=11fef089\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/COPrDNxJrSB/?igshid=1qtyu15sx2vhi</a><br />\n<br />\n嚟緊阿sir嘅作品都會參與市集，大家可以到場支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZnL29SpMbzXQY4XxcuLs9knJMGZ6bC5mcZqLNVBWKzHK?filename=f7Esmv1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff7Esmv1.png&h=07f10140&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb875c5530228a685dcd7ca98ac0f147a0e2c728","tid":2509662,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:07:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d754782b02acb99e4a97d053237ab26423aa805","tid":2509662,"uid":267225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2fcf0321ad6c261f82cdb30d7a4b699422f878","tid":2509662,"uid":1865,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"教history嘅死得啦<br />\n一，二戰咁多政治漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47215875793b742821de691ec477d88ec6e9cd4","tid":2509662,"uid":53687,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1b2fcf0321ad6c261f82cdb30d7a4b699422f878","tid":2509662,"uid":1865,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:09:11.000Z","msg":"教history嘅死得啦<br />\n一，二戰咁多政治漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:11:02.000Z","msg":"會篩走晒罵中國嗰啲漫畫"},{"pid":"a955c353ea4b6400668aee5356849b6184e9cc7b","tid":2509662,"uid":21761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7b5f02740a114c6ee4f7258780891ffcfe49af6b","tid":2509662,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:12:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4dd56466827ea182c1859f3c77037f1378385c52","tid":2509662,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"pushh"},{"pid":"8163677173b71cd9c44d1062b9d07972